'solution.desc':'Deron doesn\'t replace traditional logistics. Deron fills the gaps that legacy infrastructure can\'t reach — with autonomous drones, AI, and systems built for Vietnamese people.',
'solution.p1t':'Autonomous Flight','solution.p1d':'No pilot needed, no roads needed, no terrain obstacles. Centrally managed flight operations.',
