'whynow.desc':'The regulatory framework is becoming clearer. Technology policy is opening up. Real-world application trials have begun. And safety requirements are pushing the market into a more professional phase.',
'whynow.s1t':'Regulatory progress','whynow.s1d':'Decree 288/2025/ND-CP was issued on 05/11/2025, supplementing the management framework for UAVs from registration, operation to training and licensing.',
