'whynow.s4t':'Real-world deployments underway','whynow.s4d':'Vietnam Post piloted UAV medical transport in Hanoi. DOST HCMC coordinated with Vietnam Post and UAV companies to launch a postal UAV route connecting Can Gio – Vung Tau.',
