'about.label':'ABOUT DERON','about.title':'We didn\'t start from a market opportunity.',
'about.sub':'Deron didn\'t start from a market opportunity. Deron started from something constant — solving problems that people truly need solved.',
'about.origin':'Origin','about.whyTitle':'Why does Deron<br>exist?',
'about.why.p1':'Why is it that every rainy season, communities are no longer isolated from the world — yet remain isolated from rescue systems?',
'about.why.p2':'Why are military helicopters the only solution — not because no alternative technology exists, but because no one bothers to build it?',
'about.why.p3':'Deron was built to answer those questions. With engineering. With commitment. With Vietnamese roots.',
'about.bacgiap.caption':'General Vo Nguyen Giap',
'about.dbp.label':'Dien Bien Phu','about.dbp.title':'Inspired by<br>national spirit',
'about.dbp.p1':'Inspired by General Vo Nguyen Giap\'s words: "The time has come for new Dien Bien Phu battles" — not about war, but about the will for self-reliance.',
'about.dbp.p2':'The Dien Bien Phu campaign proved that Vietnamese people can prevail through intellect, creativity, and willpower — even facing seemingly impossible challenges.',
'about.founder.role':'Founder & Project Leader',
'about.founder.p1':'Founder of Deron, born and raised in Dak Lak — one of the most geographically complex and hard-to-reach provinces in Vietnam\'s Central Highlands.',
'about.founder.p2':'Based in Ho Chi Minh City, Harry is building Deron with a long-term vision for low-altitude logistics infrastructure — driven by real needs, not technology trends.',
'about.founder.p3':'Deron is among the few Vietnamese startups developing its own flight controller (DMA) instead of relying entirely on foreign platforms.',
'about.roadmap.label':'Roadmap','about.roadmap.title':'From prototype<br>to national infrastructure.',
