'tech.dma.desc':'DMA is a self-developed avionics system — independent of foreign platforms.','tech.dma.status':'In Development',
'tech.spec.fmu':'STM32F765 — Primary Flight Management Unit','tech.spec.io':'STM32F103 — Input/Output dedicated processor',
'tech.spec.imu':'Dual IMU — redundant inertial measurement <span class="spec-tag">Redundant</span>',
'tech.spec.baro':'Dual Barometer — altitude sensing redundancy <span class="spec-tag">Redundant</span>',
